Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配備著以電腦為導航系統的賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「CYBER F0RMULA」正式登場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替「F-l」的2l世紀賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令全世界人都狂熱起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,新世紀GPX 「CYBER F0RMULA」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:33.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:40.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:43.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:47.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自你求助的訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:53.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨夜開始一直感覺得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:01:00.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突如其來的風暴阻擋了前進的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:04.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望便浮現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:08.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜歡 是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:15.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會放在心上 不論什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:20.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的波浪會緊隨而來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:27.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上出發 決不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:33.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現夢想 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:36.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:43.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:50.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:02:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見隼人以優異的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.48,0:02:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪得全日本錦標賽第三名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且獲得超級駕照的榮譽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有資格參加在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界各國共十場的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高智能方程式賽車錦標賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十場比賽的第一場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將在美國的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼恩賽車場舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十話  世界賽開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣 武八
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在測路面的溫度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在阿斯拉達已經通過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五個測定點了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 車子狀況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是只要一個不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會摔得粉身碎骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在決賽的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是再危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也得維持平均在200km的時速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要確實記住跑道的形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢牢地記在心裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過幾秒鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要經過一個接近360度的轉彎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛的技巧是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將速度放慢 安全的通過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有騰雲駕霧的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼高的地方比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的得小心才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟日本的跑道安全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的路面是平坦的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法測知落差
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過是問一下有關路況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是伸介
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達已經通過這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過不久就會出現一條橋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要記住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡得門大橋前面的路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最容易發生事故的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見橋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會常有事故發生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為大大小小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有將近300個連續的下坡彎道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你怎麼踩剎車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有辦法達到剎車的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在通過連續彎道之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是橋上的直線加速
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後是一個600R的彎道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多車子來不及減速
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝向谷底了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達 你聽清楚了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說這什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要記住的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果不能控制自己的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達是幫不上你的忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔 用不著那麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經通過橋樑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美樹 連絡其他的人準備收隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次說這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人沒辦法完全記住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的部份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用錄影帶來解說就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備收隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了練習之外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上要大吃一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儲備體力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介 把果汁給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒吃過這麼厚的牛排
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是錦標賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一戰的預賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔 我得要向你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收回之前對你說過的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經說過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧願成為摩托車賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不要開車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:05:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是現在我想法已經改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得能成為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高智能方程式的賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是一件很不錯的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你會改變主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 我們都會支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見隼人試車的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的 不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的能夠參加世界錦標賽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 這麼好的牛排
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼都不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部吃掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會發胖的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的食量好驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要幫那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦的電腦吃一點才對嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到夢想 倒提醒了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平他到底什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才可以出院呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生說為了安全起見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得再住院觀察一兩天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還好 良平他不是孤單的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在遠處的小島上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在已經轉到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以觀看車賽的鎮上醫院去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他不會有問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會看到比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 明天就得\N拜託你代替良平了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就要開始比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在為大家播報體育新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣受全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃電霹靂車車迷所注目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界錦標賽第一場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天起將在肯尼恩賽車場舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加比賽的隊伍中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最受注目的優勝者還是羅貝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是巴西出生的天才車手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾獲得去年世界盃的冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 也很有希望奪魁的二人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分別是SGM隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛德國制
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精密機械的法蘭·哈利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及另外一個本土隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國之星的明星車手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積奇·古里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來為各位介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首次登場的兩位選手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是隼人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是有史以來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最年輕的車手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一個是剛獲得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本錦標賽冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首次向世界舞台挑戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本年輕車手新條直輝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在英國高智能方程式賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如慧星一樣出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特·修馬赫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在英國國內的車賽中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現了驚人的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個充滿神秘色彩的車手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於他不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將受過傷的臉呈現在大家面前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拒絕接受採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他一直戴著太陽眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個人要以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何種戰術來打敗前三強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位賽車迷 靜心的等待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是氣死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個跑道有高度的大落差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎還有剎車
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將承受很大的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達GSX
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是首次露面的日本機器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對那輛車子看法怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請停一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不對勁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個先到會場去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有一點事情要辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問要吃點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束以後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起到迪斯耐樂園去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 我想到好萊塢去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人不去 我們自己去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:09:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要盡全力做到最好才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第一戰中 冠軍一定是積奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊!積奇一定會打敗羅貝的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的選手都是雜種
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積奇…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要理會他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅貝跟積奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是世界超一流的選手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我們之間是有差距的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底到了什麼樣的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去以後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把他們的錄影帶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放給你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 你只是承受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種刺激的 對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 不要再鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像吃得太飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 我爸爸也會來加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 你一定要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會盡全力的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要這樣 手放開嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個都長大了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會跟大家說的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他說了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說阿斯拉達可能會遭到突襲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我們嚴加提防注意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他們還沒得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定還會再採取行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 你別太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就要開始重要的比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該好好保養身體才是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一靜下來我就會感到壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥以前也常常做這樣的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你一定要保佑我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說如果哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠來給我們加油的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定可以表現得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒有他的消息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用太擔心了 明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修哥他一定沒事的 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一流汗就想喝點冰的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去幫你拿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有人在偷看我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像戴著一付太陽眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要來對付阿斯拉達的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達是我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不許任何人碰它一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠車子才贏得第三名的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說這話是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠運氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒有辦法一直獲勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我再到那邊看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有看到什麼可疑的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 發生了什麼事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 沒什麼特別的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不是武八嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子精神蠻好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 我今天已經
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先看過跑道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國的自然環境
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟日本是完全不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說日本的自然環境
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可以讓人感到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是溫暖的母親的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼美國 就是一切讓你感到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨立自主的父親了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從美國才正式的開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我們兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起進入錦標賽的決賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:14:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有發現任何可疑的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有任何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險物品的反應信號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔 我有一個疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有人想要對付
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達GSX呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經有人說過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是企業間的間諜行為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說真的是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是也有生命的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在出發到美國之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經打電話到英國給我老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻沒有人接聽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸的確也是他們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你盡可放心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經搬到一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常安全的地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個人真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 你聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你爸爸嘔心瀝血的傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果能駕著阿斯拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出場比賽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是使你爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心的最好的辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 車田叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來接好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是管生阿斯拉達隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是隼人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 請問你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你非奪得世界盃冠軍不可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你明天預賽成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 我們暫時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不要見面比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界閃電霹靂車的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車迷們大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界盃錦標賽馬上就要開幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界各國所選拔出來的好手們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經相聚在這肯尼恩賽車場裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一場龍爭虎鬥的激烈競賽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要呈現在各位的眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預賽賽程是環繞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市區一圈的街道跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間一定要把握住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對要通過預賽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我一個人待在醫院裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在太痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 拜託你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有人說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是運氣好才能得勝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人說我是完全靠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機器的優越性能才能得勝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不管別人怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始我要展現實力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達已經進人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一個彎道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要進入計時區了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加預選的隊伍好像有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共有30隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中可以進入決賽的只有24隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經跑完的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們成績怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有十個隊伍跑完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止 最後一隊的分數是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1分39秒02
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人現在到哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把資料調出來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將要通過中間點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過中間點了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人跟阿斯拉達配合的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是完美無缺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所顯示的46秒52是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以單純的計算來講
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果隼人能以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在速度持續到終點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以輕易的突破39秒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會有37秒的優良成績呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要高興得太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的跑道裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多的轉彎道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度會慢下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的感覺特別好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會有好成績
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能維持現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡量減少時間損失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼成績會高過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經跑完的十個隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一個技術高超的賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非進入前幾名不可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:19:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快呀 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排名如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有九個隊伍還沒有跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使輸給九個隊伍也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以進入決賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特·修馬赫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以參加決賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你那種跑法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加有其他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,競爭隊伍在場的比賽\N那是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太得意忘形的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很難在比賽裏獲勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該明白才對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你未免太多管閒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副了不起的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是預賽落選
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼紅別人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見他站在那裏看我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特·修馬赫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是一位賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特·修馬赫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在預賽裏的成績
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比你還要好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔為了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭賀你通過預賽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要請我們吃一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛排大餐 我們快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃得飽飽的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他修馬赫是什麼傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.69,0:21:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要在決賽裏把他給擊敗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:16.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人目光沒有在背後注視著我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:23.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面向前方 生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為肩負著使命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:37.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下雙手 仰望天空時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:40.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:48.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容是我心中的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:55.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有現在加倍努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能有明天的輝煌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:05.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 不用後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:11.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著自己樹立的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:16.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎著風前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:21.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終我們會是勝利者

